{"tid":1382453,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"諗緊方法對付暴徒","createTime":"2019-07-29T13:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T13:20:41.000Z","uid":73518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3ffe6326fbaf02ec39032624a5a0bb702ba05e3e","tid":1382453,"uid":73518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:08:34.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多上圖先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9gV3uG9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9gV3uG9.png&h=0cfc6181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家都知最近周街都係黑衫白衫暴徒<br />\n我覺得呢種十幾二十蚊既防身棍真係要隨身攜帶<br />\n價錢唔貴 又可以保護自己  <br />\n總好過赤手空拳打人地成身裝備<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VrqOFPW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVrqOFPW.png&h=690819de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二就係類似呢種既防狼器<br />\n無論絲打定巴打都可以扣定一個係背囊<br />\n防止落單既時候被暴徒捉去暗角打都無人知<br />\n聽講一撳會響到仆街<br />\n就算你d friend忙緊過唔到黎幫手<br />\n至少引到記者過黎影低所有嘢先<br />\n<br />\n其實呢兩樣都好抵好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔想再見到作為良好市民既大家比人用不對等既武力打<br />\n以上既嘢可能有人講過，但係覺得呢d係後排既發夢人士都可以自備，所以試下開post啦"},{"pid":"0be698fbd3adace12dbf802e7fffdbb0b7cef4cc","tid":1382453,"uid":259302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:12:42.000Z","msg":"買伸縮棍前查清楚香港法例先"},{"pid":"33de704631adab97fd97e196ddbf7af20e0608f0","tid":1382453,"uid":11937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:20:41.000Z","msg":"互相推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「全港大罷工」動搖唔到經濟民生佔晒全香港都無用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dsovuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dsovuS</a>"}]}